<text><body>
<pb ed="F" id="F12.0546.0092b" n="0092b"/>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><div1 type="w"><byline type="Collector">通理大師集</byline>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b02"/><juan fun="open" n="1"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead>金剛&CB17716;一本</jhead></juan><p id="pF12p0092b0206" place="inline" rend="margin-left:2em">作供梵嘆如常依慈氏&CB17716;聲</p>
<table cols="5">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b03"/><row><cell rows="9">志心&CB08221;命&CB17716;</cell><cell>法身非相</cell><cell>應化非真</cell><cell>福智無比</cell><cell>無為福勝</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b04"/><row><cell>一相無相</cell><cell>化無所化</cell><cell>無&CB07589;無滅</cell><cell>法界通化</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b05"/><row><cell>莊嚴淨土</cell><cell>如理實見</cell><cell>離色離見</cell><cell>一切佛寶</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b06"/><row><cell>善現起請</cell><cell>尊重正教</cell><cell>無法可得</cell><cell>依法出生</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b07"/><row><cell>一&CB17716;合相</cell><cell>法會因由</cell><cell>大乘正宗</cell><cell>無德無說</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b08"/><row><cell>持經功德</cell><cell>如法受持</cell><cell>非說所說</cell><cell>一切法寶</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b09"/><row><cell>妙行無住</cell><cell>正信希有</cell><cell>離相寂滅</cell><cell>能淨業障</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b10"/><row><cell>一&CB00816;同觀</cell><cell>威儀寂靜</cell><cell>究竟無我</cell><cell>知見不生</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b11"/><row><cell>淨心行善</cell><cell>不愛不貪</cell><cell>無諍三昧</cell><cell>一切僧寶</cell></row></table>
<table cols="5">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b12"/><row><cell rows="2">志心普奉為</cell><cell>三十二分滿</cell><cell>一十八住圓</cell><cell>二十七疑遣</cell><cell>德海難思議</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b13"/><row><cell>四恩并七趣</cell><cell>法界諸群生</cell><cell>罪障皆消滅</cell><cell>速圓般若海</cell></row></table>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b14"/><p type="head1" id="pF12p0092b1401">志心懺悔</p>
<table cols="5">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b15"/><row><cell rows="2">志心普懺願</cell><cell>先身有報障</cell><cell>今日受持經</cell><cell>暫被人輕賤</cell><cell>轉重復還輕</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b16"/><row><cell>唯願八金剛</cell><cell>清淨四菩薩</cell><cell>我今與眾生</cell><cell>速圓般若海</cell></row></table>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b17"/><p type="head1" id="pF12p0092b1701">唱處世界</p>
<table cols="4">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b18"/><row><cell>處世界如虛空</cell><cell>如蓮花不著水</cell><cell>心清淨超於彼</cell><cell>&CB30397;首&CB17716;無上尊</cell></row></table>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b19"/><p type="head1" id="pF12p0092b1901">吟迴向偈</p>
<table cols="2">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b20"/><row><cell>我以普賢殊勝行</cell><cell>無邊勝福皆迴向</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b21"/><row><cell>普願沈溺諸眾生</cell><cell>速往無量光佛所</cell></row></table>
<table cols="5">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b22"/><row><cell rows="3">志心普命</cell><cell>十身無礙佛</cell><cell>法報化三身</cell><cell></cell><cell></cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b23"/><row><cell>十藏甚深法</cell><cell>戒定慧三乘</cell><cell>願共諸眾生</cell><cell>皆共成佛道</cell></row>
<lb ed="F" n="0092b24"/><row><cell>十地聖賢僧</cell><cell>上中下三根</cell><cell></cell><cell></cell></row></table>
<table cols="4">
<lb ed="F" n="0092b25"/><row><cell>&CB17716;懺&CB08221;依竟</cell><cell>所集諸聖因</cell><cell>施一切群生</cell><cell>皆共成佛道</cell></row></table></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
